        <h4 id="q10">This thing chews my batteries!</h4>

        <p>If you're using this on mobile and find it's using a lot of battery, try switching to a lower bitrate stream and turning the DSP settings off - the DSP is fairly lightweight, but will still be using extra CPU cycles on top of the regular audio rendering.</p>

